WEBVTT

01:21.360 --> 01:25.524
Captions made possible by
HOME BOX OFFICE

01:25.530 --> 01:29.626
A Division of TIME WARNER
ENTERTAINMENT COMPANY, LP.

02:54.060 --> 02:57.223
SO YOU'RE BACK
FROM OUTER SPACE

02:57.230 --> 02:58.959
( laughing )

02:58.960 --> 03:02.088
THAT LOOK
UPON YOUR FACE

03:02.100 --> 03:03.658
AH!

03:03.660 --> 03:06.151
I AM SUCH
A FUCKING IDIOT !

03:06.160 --> 03:08.822
I SHOULD'VE DUMPED HIM
YEARS AGO.

03:08.830 --> 03:11.799
I FEEL
20 POUNDS LIGHTER.

03:11.800 --> 03:14.496
MORE LIKE
180 POUNDS.

03:15.900 --> 03:17.856
WHAT DO YOU THINK
HE'S DOING TONIGHT ?

03:17.860 --> 03:20.192
OH, HE'S FUCKING HIS
LITTLE GRAD STUDENT.

03:20.200 --> 03:21.997
THINKING HE'S KING
OF THE WORLD !

03:22.000 --> 03:25.925
GOD, I WISH I KNEW
WHO INVENTED VIAGRA.

03:25.930 --> 03:27.557
SO, I COULD
SHOOT HIM.

03:27.560 --> 03:29.357
I'LL DRINK
TO THAT.

03:29.360 --> 03:30.622
HEAR, HEAR !

03:30.630 --> 03:32.598
OH, SHIT, IT FELL
DOWN MY SHIRT.

03:32.600 --> 03:34.454
HOLD THIS, HOLD THIS,
I HAVE AN IDEA.

03:34.460 --> 03:35.495
WAIT.

03:35.500 --> 03:36.956
DRIVER !

03:36.960 --> 03:38.655
HEY, DRIVER !

03:38.660 --> 03:41.697
TAKE US TO MYAGI'S,
OKAY ?

03:41.700 --> 03:44.157
'CAUSE I FEEL
LIKE DANCING !

03:44.160 --> 03:45.422
OOH, LOOK
WHAT I FOUND.

03:45.430 --> 03:47.819
( laughing )

03:50.060 --> 03:51.095
PROMISE ME,

03:51.100 --> 03:52.749
NO DANCING ON
THE TABLES TONIGHT.

03:52.760 --> 03:54.318
YOU JUST
OPEN THIS !

04:00.800 --> 04:03.451
COME BACK DOWN,
HONEY.

04:04.460 --> 04:06.428
I'M KING
OF THE WORLD !

04:06.430 --> 04:08.819
I'M KING OF
THE WORLD.

04:08.830 --> 04:10.422
I'M KING
OF THE WORLD !

04:45.200 --> 04:47.851
THIS IS HOW YOU STUDY FOR THE
FUNERAL DIRECTOR'S LICENSE ?

04:47.860 --> 04:50.852
YOU MUST REALLY LIKE
WEARING A SUIT.

04:50.860 --> 04:53.055
THERE'S ALWAYS A CHANCE
WE MIGHT GET A WALK-IN.

04:53.060 --> 04:56.029
THERE'S ALWAYS A CHANCE
WE MIGHT GET ABDUCTED BY ALIENS.

05:01.100 --> 05:03.591
WHAT'S THE LONGEST WE'VE
EVER GONE WITHOUT A BODY ?

05:03.600 --> 05:07.092
I REMEMBER DAD SAYING
SOMETHING LIKE NINE DAYS,

05:07.100 --> 05:08.795
DURING THE '84 OLYMPICS.

05:08.800 --> 05:10.893
"THE GREAT DROUGHT
OF '84."

05:10.900 --> 05:13.528
YOU REMEMBER HOW DAD
USED TO DO WALTER BRENNAN.

05:13.530 --> 05:15.828
"COME ON, LI'I'I'LE LUKE,
LET'S STITCH THIS DEAD GUY UP

05:15.830 --> 05:17.821
"'CAUSE MAW'S
MADE A MESS OF CATFISH

05:17.830 --> 05:19.320
AND I'M POWERFUL
#SHUNGRY."

05:22.730 --> 05:24.925
OKAY, WELL, THANK YOU FOR
MAKING ME FEEL LIKE AN IDIOT.

05:24.930 --> 05:26.352
NO, I JUST...

05:26.360 --> 05:28.999
YOU KNEW A WHOLE SIDE
OF DAD I NEVER DID.

05:31.700 --> 05:32.928
NINE DAYS, HUH ?

05:32.930 --> 05:34.727
WE JUST MIGHT
BEAT THAT.

05:34.730 --> 05:37.756
"WHEN A FAMILY PLACES MONEY IN
A FUNERAL TRUST FOR A PRE-NEED,

05:37.760 --> 05:39.796
"HOW MUCH MONEY CAN
THE FUNERAL HOME USE

05:39.800 --> 05:41.791
"FOR OTHER PURPOSES
UNTIL THE FAMILY REQUIRES

05:41.800 --> 05:43.199
YOUR SERVICES ?"

05:43.200 --> 05:44.792
500/0.

05:46.200 --> 05:47.599
25% ?

05:47.600 --> 05:48.749
ZERO, NONE.

05:48.760 --> 05:49.954
I KNEW THAT.

05:49.960 --> 05:51.621
( phone )

05:52.860 --> 05:53.997
HELLO ?

05:54.000 --> 05:55.797
( Brenda )
Hey, it's me.

05:55.800 --> 05:56.926
WELL, IT'S ABOUT TIME.

05:56.930 --> 05:58.397
I'VE ONLY BEEN CALLING YOU
FOR SIX DAYS STRAIGHT.

05:58.400 --> 06:00.459
Yeah, I've been
incredibly busy.

06:00.460 --> 06:01.791
LOTS OF NEW
CLIENTS, SORRY.

06:01.800 --> 06:02.892
How's Billy ?

06:02.900 --> 06:04.458
UH, BETTER.

06:04.460 --> 06:06.997
IT ONLY HAPPENS
ONCE A YEAR, YOU KNOW ?

06:07.000 --> 06:08.797
TWICE AT THE MOST.

06:08.800 --> 06:10.427
SO, WHEN CAN
I SEE YOU ?

06:10.430 --> 06:11.988
I don't know...

06:12.000 --> 06:14.093
Tuesday ?

06:14.100 --> 06:15.920
IS HE STAYING
WITH YOU ?

06:15.930 --> 06:18.023
YEAH, JUST FOR
A FEW MORE DAYS.

06:18.030 --> 06:18.894
LISTEN, I GO'I'I'A GO.

06:18.900 --> 06:20.720
I'LL CALL YOU, OKAY ?
I PROMISE.

06:23.130 --> 06:25.951
WE THINK WE'RE WEIRD,
BEING UNDERTAKER'S KIDS ?

06:25.960 --> 06:28.793
JUST BE THANKFUL OUR PARENTS
WEREN'T FUCKING SHRINKS.

06:28.800 --> 06:30.028
"HOW MANY DAYS DOES
A FAMILY HAVE

06:30.030 --> 06:31.952
TO CANCEL A CONTRACT
FOR SERVICES ?"

06:31.960 --> 06:34.099
I GET SO SICK OF
THIS BIZARRE BEHAVIOR

06:34.100 --> 06:35.556
THAT I'M SUPPOSED
TO FIGURE OUT.

06:35.560 --> 06:36.720
AND THEN SHE SEEMS
PISSED OFF WHEN I CAN'T.

06:36.730 --> 06:37.754
IT'S FUCKING
NEUROTIC !

06:37.760 --> 06:39.057
WOULD YOU CONCENTRATE
ON THIS, PLEASE ?

06:39.060 --> 06:40.652
I NEED YOU TO
GET YOUR LICENSE,

06:40.660 --> 06:42.651
SO, YOU CAN START HANDLING
YOUR SHARE OF THINGS.

06:42.660 --> 06:43.752
"HOW MANY DAYS--"

06:43.760 --> 06:45.625
TH REE DAYS.

06:45.630 --> 06:45.698
IT'S NOT EXACTLY
THE CALIFORNIA BAR, DAVID.

06:47.830 --> 06:49.320
COME ON...

06:49.330 --> 06:51.252
MAKE ME EARN IT.

06:51.260 --> 06:53.558
"WHEN A FUNERAL HOME
ADVERTISES THEIR SERVICES,

06:53.560 --> 06:55.949
"WHICH TWO SPECIFIC
PIECES OF INFORMATION

06:55.960 --> 06:58.929
ARE LEGALLY REQUIRED
ON ALL ADVERTISEMENTS ?"

07:06.700 --> 07:09.794
I'D START WITH SOME
HEAW DUTY ARMATURE MATERIAL

07:09.800 --> 07:11.097
AND PLASTER OF PARIS.

07:11.100 --> 07:13.989
MASTIC COMPOUND
FOR HER FACE,

07:14.000 --> 07:17.356
TISSUE BUILDER AND WAX
FOR HER FEATURES.

07:19.060 --> 07:21.153
I'D FINISH HER OFF
WITH A GOOD SEALER,

07:21.160 --> 07:23.549
SHE'LL LEAK
LIKE A GARDEN HOSE.

07:23.560 --> 07:26.427
A LITTLE AIRBRUSHING
AND A HIGH QUALITY FOUNDATION

07:26.430 --> 07:27.920
AND SHE'S GOOD TO GO.

07:27.930 --> 07:30.649
HOW MUCH TIME
WOULD YOU NEED ?

07:30.660 --> 07:33.629
AT LEAST A DAY
TO DO IT RIGHT.

07:33.630 --> 07:36.292
THE FISHERS CAN SPARE YOU
FOR A FULL DAY ?

07:36.300 --> 07:38.928
I'M NOT AUDITIONING
FOR YOU.

07:38.930 --> 07:41.490
THIS IS A ONE-TIME
FREELANCE JOB

07:41.500 --> 07:43.058
AND I USE
MY OWN MATERIALS.

07:43.060 --> 07:44.891
KROEHNER'S TEXTURIZERS,
THEY BLOW.

07:44.900 --> 07:45.855
HOW MUCH ?

07:45.860 --> 07:46.849
$1500.

07:46.860 --> 07:49.454
OKAY.

07:51.800 --> 07:53.199
FOR SOMEONE
WITH YOUR TALENT,

07:53.200 --> 07:55.054
THAT'S A BARGAIN.

07:56.430 --> 07:58.591
STOP BLOWING
SMOKE UP MY ASS.

07:58.600 --> 08:02.058
I'M NOT QUI'I'I'ING
THE FISHERS.

08:02.060 --> 08:04.096
MR. F. PUT ME
THROUGH SCHOOL.

08:04.100 --> 08:05.920
HAVE HER DONE
BY FIVE.

08:05.930 --> 08:08.023
AND SHE'D BETTER
LOOK FLAWLESS.

08:11.430 --> 08:13.648
( male )
DON'T THINK ABOUT
HOW STEEP IT IS.

08:13.660 --> 08:16.754
YOU'VE GOT EIGHT
MORE MILES.

08:18.200 --> 08:20.452
COME ON,
KEEP IT MOVING.

08:22.030 --> 08:23.952
CARLOS CASTANEDA
WROTE,

08:23.960 --> 08:26.155
"A WARRIOR TAKES HIS LOT,
WHATEVER IT MAY BE,

08:26.160 --> 08:29.197
AND ACCEPTS IT IN
ULTIMATE HUMBLENESS."

08:29.200 --> 08:31.452
YEAH, WELL...

08:32.460 --> 08:34.951
CARLOS CASTANEDA
CAN BLOW ME.

08:34.960 --> 08:36.621
TELL ME ABOUT IT.

08:36.630 --> 08:38.052
WHERE'S THE WHOLE

08:38.060 --> 08:40.358
"SPIRITUAL TRANSCENDENCE"
PART FROM THE BROCHURE ?

08:40.360 --> 08:42.897
THIS IS LIKE
FUCKING BOOT CAMP.

08:42.900 --> 08:46.358
HAVE I THANKED YOU FOR
GETTING ME HIGH THIS MORNING ?

08:46.360 --> 08:48.328
LIKE 12 TIMES.

08:48.330 --> 08:50.252
JUST MAKING SURE.

08:51.000 --> 08:52.524
CLAIRE, TOPHER !

08:52.530 --> 08:54.327
YOU'RE STRAGGLING.

08:54.330 --> 08:55.558
YOU KNOW THE RULES.

08:55.560 --> 08:57.289
THE GROUP
STAYS TOGETHER.

08:57.300 --> 08:58.653
PERIOD.

08:58.660 --> 09:01.197
JA VOL,
MEIN COMMANDANT.

09:04.030 --> 09:05.554
I GOT A NEW WAY
TO MAKE MONEY.

09:05.560 --> 09:07.391
WE RENT OUT THE SLUMBER ROOM
FOR MEETINGS.

09:07.400 --> 09:08.856
12 STEP GROUPS,
THAT SORT OF THING.

09:08.860 --> 09:10.020
ARE YOU INSANE ?

09:10.030 --> 09:12.248
DRUNKS AND DRUG ADDICTS
INSIDE OUR HOME ?

09:12.260 --> 09:13.625
THE INSURANCE
ISSUES ALONE.

09:13.630 --> 09:15.427
WELL, THEN HOW ABOUT
SENIOR DANCE LESSONS ?

09:15.430 --> 09:17.318
TWICE A WEEK AT
50 BUCKS A POP.

09:17.330 --> 09:18.797
THAT'S $5200 A YEAR,

09:18.800 --> 09:19.994
THAT'S SIX MONTHS'
PROPERTY TAX.

09:20.000 --> 09:21.092
WHAT IF WE'VE
GOT A VIEWING ?

09:21.100 --> 09:23.091
THEY WORK AROUND
OUR SCHEDULE.

09:23.100 --> 09:24.590
DAVID, THESE OLD PEOPLE
HAVE NOTHING ELSE TO DO.

09:24.600 --> 09:26.158
THEY DANCE HERE TWICE
A WEEK, HAVE FUN.

09:26.160 --> 09:28.458
WHO DO YOU THINK GETS
THE CALL WHEN THEY DROP ?

09:28.460 --> 09:30.849
THAT'S ACTUALLY
NOT A BAD IDEA.

09:30.860 --> 09:32.327
WELL, GOOD, BECAUSE
THEY'RE COMING HERE AT TWO.

09:32.330 --> 09:34.093
SO, NO MORE COMMENTS
ABOUT ME NOT PULLING MY WEIGHT

09:34.100 --> 09:36.022
FOR A WHILE,
OKAY ?

09:43.030 --> 09:45.225
SO, IS THIS A NEW
COMPANY POLICY,
CASUAL FRIDAYS ?

09:45.230 --> 09:47.448
NICE OF YOU TO DROP BY,
IT'S ALMOST NOON.

09:47.460 --> 09:48.654
AND I STAYED 'TIL
AFTER NINE LAST NIGHT,

09:48.660 --> 09:49.854
RESTOCKING
AND STERILIZING.

09:49.860 --> 09:51.350
YOU MEAN,
YOU DIDN'T CHECK ?

09:51.360 --> 09:52.918
LOOK, IF IT'S ALRIGHT
WITH YOU GUYS,

09:52.930 --> 09:54.625
I NEED THE DAY OFF.

09:54.630 --> 09:55.892
VAN ESSA'S GOT
AN ULTRASOUND.

09:55.900 --> 09:57.197
SHE JUST HAD
ONE LAST WEEK.

09:57.200 --> 09:58.724
THEY JUST WANT TO
DO ANOTHER ONE.

09:58.730 --> 10:01.358
I THINK I SHOULD BE THERE
WITH HER, DON'T YOU ?

10:01.360 --> 10:02.657
WELL, OF COURSE,
YOU COULD'VE JUST CALLED.

10:02.660 --> 10:04.298
I LEFT MY JACKET
IN THE PREP ROOM.

10:04.300 --> 10:07.053
IT'S GOT MY WALLET,
MY INSURANCE CARD,
ALL THAT STUFF.

10:07.060 --> 10:08.493
THAN KS, GUYS.

10:09.300 --> 10:11.427
GREAT, ONCE AGAIN
I'M THE ASSHOLE

10:11.430 --> 10:13.227
AND YOU'RE
THE COOL GUY.

10:13.230 --> 10:15.323
WELL, YOU CAN TELL HIM TOMORROW
THAT HE'S CLEANING OUT

10:15.330 --> 10:16.695
THE BODY FRIDGE.

10:16.700 --> 10:17.928
I WANT IT SCRUBBED
AND HOSED AND DISINFECTED.

10:17.930 --> 10:18.919
YOU TELL HIM.

10:18.930 --> 10:20.352
IT'S FISHER & SONS.

10:20.360 --> 10:22.248
SOMETIMES YOU HAVE TO
BE THE BAD COP.

10:22.260 --> 10:24.626
WELL, YOU'RE SO
GOOD AT IT.

10:24.630 --> 10:26.291
(vacuum running )

10:38.660 --> 10:40.423
RICO !

10:43.230 --> 10:44.720
NATE, PLEASE.

10:44.730 --> 10:46.027
DON'T DO THAT.

10:46.030 --> 10:47.759
I GOT A LOT
ON MY MIND

10:47.760 --> 10:49.421
WITH THE ULTRASOUND
AND ALL, YOU KNOW ?

10:49.430 --> 10:51.057
DAVID WANTS YOU
TO CLEAN OUT THE--

10:51.060 --> 10:52.857
THE WALK-IN,
I KNOW, I KNOW.

10:52.860 --> 10:55.192
YOUR BROTHER'S GOT A BUG
UP HIS ASS ABOUT CLEANLINESS.

10:55.200 --> 10:57.953
I KNOW, WHEN WE USED TO
PLAY G-I JOES

10:57.960 --> 10:59.928
HE ALWAYS WANTED TO
GIVE HIS A SHOWER.

11:01.800 --> 11:03.119
YEAH, WELL.

11:03.130 --> 11:04.791
I'M RUNNING LATE.

11:04.800 --> 11:06.722
WHERE'S YOUR JACKET ?

11:08.230 --> 11:09.959
OH, SHIT.

11:09.960 --> 11:11.689
MUST'VE LEFT IT
AT HOME.

11:11.700 --> 11:13.156
OH.

11:13.160 --> 11:15.355
TOLD YOU, MAN, I GOT A LOT
ON MY MIND FROM THE ULTRASOUND.

11:15.360 --> 11:17.555
SEE YA.
SEE YA.

11:26.830 --> 11:29.151
NOW, BEGINS THE VISION QUEST
PART OF OUR JOURNEY.

11:29.160 --> 11:31.594
OH, GREAT, NOW WE GET TO
STARVE AND SWEAT OURSELVES

11:31.600 --> 11:34.319
INTO A HALLUCINOGENIC
STATE OF ECSTASY.

11:34.330 --> 11:35.752
IT'S GONNA GET
HARDER AND HARDER

11:35.760 --> 11:36.988
FOR THE NEXT
COUPLE OF DAYS.

11:37.000 --> 11:39.355
YOU ALL KNOW
HOW TOUGH PHYSICALLY.

11:39.360 --> 11:42.397
NOW THE MENTAL
CHALLENGES BEGIN.

11:42.400 --> 11:46.052
OKAY, STARTING NOW,
YOU GUYS LEAD.

11:46.060 --> 11:47.823
I JUST FOLLOW.

11:47.830 --> 11:48.899
SO...

11:48.900 --> 11:51.698
I HOPE, FOR MY SAKE,
YOU'VE ALL PERFECT ED

11:51.700 --> 11:54.328
YOUR MAP
AND COMPASS SKILLS.

11:54.900 --> 11:55.650
PARKER.

11:55.660 --> 11:58.128
WHICH WAY DO WE GO ?

11:58.130 --> 11:59.051
UM...

12:01.630 --> 12:03.393
THAT WAY.

12:04.500 --> 12:05.455
WHAT ARE YOU
WAITING FOR ?

12:05.460 --> 12:06.688
YOU LEAD.

12:08.030 --> 12:09.793
FUCKING GIRL SCOUT.

12:20.100 --> 12:21.328
( female )
GOOD CALL, PARKER.

12:21.330 --> 12:23.195
SO, WHO DO YOU
THINK PLAYS PARKER

12:23.200 --> 12:24.622
IN THE MOVIE
OF HER LIFE ?

12:24.630 --> 12:26.655
SANDY BULLOCK
OR JULIA ROBERTS ?

12:26.660 --> 12:28.753
PLEASE, SHE'D NEVER
RATE THAT HIGH.

12:28.760 --> 12:32.719
SHE'D GET ONE OF THOSE
"BUFFY" OR "DAWSON'S CREEK"
CHICKS, TOPS.

12:35.130 --> 12:36.427
WHAT IS THAT ?

12:36.430 --> 12:37.624
THIS ?

12:37.630 --> 12:39.222
KHINKALI.

12:39.230 --> 12:41.027
IT'S LIKE...

12:41.030 --> 12:45.126
DUMPLING WITH
SPICY MEAT INSIDE.

12:45.130 --> 12:48.952
I CANNOT BELIEVE YOU
NEVER HEAR OF KHINKALI.

12:48.960 --> 12:50.757
YOU KNOW,

12:50.760 --> 12:53.320
YOU NEED TO GO OUT
FROM THE HOUSE MORE.

12:53.330 --> 12:54.422
I GET OUT.

12:54.430 --> 12:56.125
I TOOK A VERY ENJOYABLE TRIP
TO SAN BERNADINO

12:56.130 --> 12:57.757
JUST A FEW
WEEKS AGO.

12:57.760 --> 12:59.159
YOU SHOULD COME TO
MY NEIGHBORHOOD.

12:59.160 --> 13:00.889
ALL RUSSIAN.

13:00.900 --> 13:02.026
YOU WOULD LOVE IT.

13:02.030 --> 13:04.692
PEOPLE WITH PASSION,
FULL OF LIFE.

13:04.700 --> 13:06.156
NOT LIKE YOUR FAMILY.

13:06.160 --> 13:07.229
WHAT DO YOU MEAN ?

13:07.230 --> 13:09.755
RUSSIANS SPEAK FROM HERE,
FROM THE HEART,

13:09.760 --> 13:11.159
WITH THEIR SOULS.

13:11.160 --> 13:14.049
NOT LIKE FISHER,
LIKE FROM HERE,
LIKE LITTLE MOUSE...

13:16.930 --> 13:18.818
IF IT'S SO WONDERFUL
IN RUSSIA,

13:18.830 --> 13:20.923
YOU SHOULD TAKE
THE FIRST FLIGHT BACK.

13:20.930 --> 13:24.457
IN RUSSIA,
I WAS ENGINEER.

13:25.760 --> 13:27.489
KNOCK-KNOCK.

13:27.500 --> 13:29.024
HIRAM.

13:29.030 --> 13:31.055
I TRIED MY HAND AT
JAMAICAN JERK CHICKEN.

13:31.060 --> 13:32.288
TURNED OUT GOOD.

13:32.300 --> 13:33.528
THOUGHT YOU MIGHT
LIKE SOME FOR LUNCH.

13:33.530 --> 13:34.997
THAT'S SO
THOUGHTFU L.

13:35.000 --> 13:36.729
THANK YOU.

13:38.060 --> 13:41.552
HIRAM, THIS IS
MY BOSS, NIKOLAI.

13:41.560 --> 13:43.494
SHE HAS A LUNCH.

13:43.500 --> 13:44.797
HERE, TRY SOME.

13:44.800 --> 13:45.653
PLEASE.

13:45.660 --> 13:47.389
YOU BURN ED IT.

13:47.400 --> 13:49.095
NIKOLAI.

13:49.100 --> 13:50.453
RUTH IS BUSY.

13:50.460 --> 13:52.690
I'M ON
MY LUNCH BREAK.

13:52.700 --> 13:54.429
LUNCH IS OVER.

13:54.430 --> 13:56.295
NOW WE WORK.

14:00.700 --> 14:02.918
SORRY I GOT YOU IN TROUBLE
WITH YOUR BOSS.

14:02.930 --> 14:05.296
DON'T YOU WORRY,
I CAN HANDLE HIM.

14:07.330 --> 14:09.651
( square dance music playing )

14:16.030 --> 14:17.827
EVERYBODY READY...

14:17.830 --> 14:19.559
AND OUT AND LEFT...

14:23.400 --> 14:24.890
GOOD, GOOD...

14:24.900 --> 14:26.959
SWING YOUR PARTNERS...

14:30.800 --> 14:32.222
AND PROMENADE HOME.

14:32.600 --> 14:34.249
VERY GOOD.

14:35.130 --> 14:36.757
HEY, VANESSA,

14:36.760 --> 14:37.920
IS RICO THERE ?

14:37.930 --> 14:39.249
No, should
I page him ?

14:39.260 --> 14:40.659
NO, IT'S NOTHING
IMPORTANT,

14:40.660 --> 14:41.695
I JUST WANTED TO RUN
SOMETHING BY HIM.

14:41.700 --> 14:43.156
Okay.

14:43.160 --> 14:44.252
HEY, DID YOU HAVE
YOUR ULTRASOUND ALREADY ?

14:44.260 --> 14:45.727
Yeah, last week.

14:45.730 --> 14:48.290
YOU'RE NOT HAVING
ONE TODAY ?

14:49.560 --> 14:53.496
OH, YEAH, YEAH, BUT NOT
'TIL THIS AFTERNOON.

14:53.500 --> 14:55.456
Huh.

14:55.460 --> 14:57.394
I'M SORRY, NATE,
THE U.P.S. GUY'S AT THE DOOR,
I GOTTA GO.

14:57.400 --> 15:00.028
AND I'LL TELL RICO
YOU CALLED, OKAY ?

15:01.230 --> 15:02.390
SHIT !

15:02.400 --> 15:03.594
SHIT.

15:03.600 --> 15:04.851
HEY !

15:04.860 --> 15:07.727
DON'T SAY THAT, PAPITO,
THAT'S A GROWN-UP WORD.

15:11.900 --> 15:13.697
( square dance music )

15:20.630 --> 15:23.690
OKAY, VERY GOOD, VERY GOOD,
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN.

15:23.700 --> 15:25.292
NOW, IF I COULD
HAVE YOUR ATTENTION

15:25.300 --> 15:26.722
FOR JUST ONE SECOND.

15:26.730 --> 15:28.220
I WANNA TEACH YOU A NEW FIGURE
FOR THE REPERTOIRE.

15:28.230 --> 15:29.697
YOU'RE GONNA
LOVE IT.

15:29.700 --> 15:30.951
YOUR FRIENDS ARE GONNA
BE VERY IMPRESSED.

15:30.960 --> 15:32.291
