YOU GOOGLIE.

46:25.530 --> 46:27.259
DRONGO.

46:47.460 --> 46:49.621
WHEN WAS
THAT TAKEN ?

46:49.630 --> 46:51.097
TWO SUMMERS AGO.

46:51.100 --> 46:52.556
IN PERTH.

46:52.560 --> 46:54.790
I THOUGHT YOU SAID YOU HADN'T
SEEN HIM IN, IN, IN...

46:54.800 --> 46:56.256
A DECADE.

46:56.260 --> 47:00.151
NO, I SAID CONNOR HASN'T
BEEN TO L.A. IN A DECADE.

47:00.160 --> 47:01.889
ALRIGHT, WHERE DO
YOU SLEEP, MATE ?

47:01.900 --> 47:05.256
'CAUSE THAT SLEEPING BAG
HASN'T MOVED AN INCH IN DAYS !

47:05.260 --> 47:06.898
THEY SLEEP IN
THE SAME BED,
WHERE ELSE ?

47:06.900 --> 47:09.789
DON'T CRACK A FIT,
NATE, MATE.

47:09.800 --> 47:12.894
I MEAN, SHE'S TOTALLY
WRAPPED UP IN YOU.

47:12.900 --> 47:15.858
OH, YOU JUST SHUT
THE FUCK UP, COWBOY !

47:15.860 --> 47:17.589
OKAY, OKAY,
I DIDN'T TELL YOU

47:17.600 --> 47:19.329
BECAUSE I KNEW YOU'D
REACT JUST LIKE THIS.

47:19.330 --> 47:21.548
WELL, HOW ELSE AM
I SUPPOSED TO REACT ?!

47:21.560 --> 47:23.994
OH SO, I'M SUPPOSED TO MAKE
AN OLD FRIEND SLEEP ON THE FLOOR

47:24.000 --> 47:25.820
JUST TO PROTECT
YOUR MACHO PRIDE ?

47:25.830 --> 47:27.422
YOU HAVE
A SHIATSU MAT.

47:27.430 --> 47:29.318
COME ON, MAN, HAVEN'T YOU
EVER SLEPT WITH A WOMAN

47:29.330 --> 47:30.729
AND NOT HAD
SEX WITH HER ?

47:34.330 --> 47:36.093
NO!

47:36.100 --> 47:38.295
OUTSIDE,
GET SOME AIR.

47:38.300 --> 47:41.428
GO OUTSIDE,
GET SOME AIR.

47:41.430 --> 47:43.022
FUCK YOU !

47:43.030 --> 47:44.952
I'M LEAVING !

47:48.800 --> 47:52.349
HAVE FUN WITH YOUR AUSSIE
FUCK MATE, FUCKER !

47:53.930 --> 47:55.693
( moaning )

48:04.400 --> 48:06.994
DAMN, YOU ARE
VERSATILE.

48:12.160 --> 48:15.152
SO, YOU THINK I'M BEING
A POSSESSIVE ASSHOLE

48:15.160 --> 48:16.991
FOR WANTING
BRENDA FOR MYSELF ?

48:17.000 --> 48:18.456
WANTING TO FEEL CONNECTED
WITH SOMEONE

48:18.460 --> 48:20.451
DOESN'T MEAN YOU'RE POSSESSIVE,
OR AN ASSHOLE.

48:20.460 --> 48:22.325
BUT UNTIL THERE'S
A COMMITMENT,

48:22.330 --> 48:23.820
YOU HAVE NO
CLAIM ON HER.

48:23.830 --> 48:26.594
A WOMAN DOESN'T HAVE TO
WAIT TO BE CHOSEN ANYMORE.

48:26.600 --> 48:28.556
NOW SHE CAN
DO THE CHOOSING.

48:28.560 --> 48:29.788
YEAH, BUT IF SHE
WAITS TOO LONG,

48:29.800 --> 48:31.495
THE RIGHT GUY MIGHT
JUST MOVE ON.

48:31.500 --> 48:33.456
YOU'RE RIGHT, DEAR.

48:33.460 --> 48:35.428
YOU'RE SO RIGHT.

48:35.430 --> 48:38.797
A CHARTERED BUS OUT OF VEGAS
OVERTURNED ON THE 10 LAST NIGHT.

48:40.630 --> 48:42.951
44 PASSENGERS.

48:42.960 --> 48:45.099
MOST OF THEM DEAD.

48:45.100 --> 48:47.921
DID YOU SLEEP
WELL LAST NIGHT ?

48:47.930 --> 48:49.329
YES, THANK YOU.

48:49.330 --> 48:51.389
YOU SLEEP AT
ALL LAST NIGHT ?

48:52.430 --> 48:54.398
HOW'D THE FUNERAL
DIRECTOR'S TEST GO ?

48:54.400 --> 48:56.049
OH, MAN, I CHOKED.

48:56.060 --> 48:57.459
WHAT A CLUSTER FUCK.

48:57.460 --> 48:58.620
LANGUAGE.

48:58.630 --> 49:00.120
YOU JUST
SAID ASSHOLE.

49:00.130 --> 49:01.495
NATE, I NEED YOU
TO PASS THAT TEST.

49:01.500 --> 49:02.990
YEAH, WELL, DAVE,

49:03.000 --> 49:05.059
I NEED YOU TO LIGHTEN UP
ON ME, STARTING NOW.

49:10.930 --> 49:12.397
HEY.

49:13.060 --> 49:15.620
FIRST OF ALL, I JUST
WANT TO THANK YOU GUYS

49:15.630 --> 49:17.495
FOR EVERYTHING THAT
YOU'VE DONE FOR ME.

49:17.500 --> 49:19.195
BUT I THINK IT'S TIME
FOR ME TO MOVE ON.

49:19.200 --> 49:22.556
I HAVE TO THINK
ABOUT MY FUTURE.

49:22.560 --> 49:24.425
MY FAMILY'S FUTURE.

49:24.430 --> 49:25.499
YOU'RE LEAVING US ?

49:25.500 --> 49:26.797
OH, DEAR.

49:26.800 --> 49:28.995
YOU HAVEN'T EVEN GIVEN US
A CHANCE TO COUNTER KROEHNER'S--

49:29.000 --> 49:31.093
AM I A PARTNER ?

49:36.800 --> 49:40.099
YOU GUYS DIDN'T
EVEN TALK ABOUT IT.

49:45.200 --> 49:46.792
THANK YOU,
FEDERICO.

49:46.800 --> 49:50.588
I'M SORRY THAT
WE CAN'T OFFER YOU MORE.

49:53.560 --> 49:56.529
YOU WILL ALWAYS HAVE A JOB
WAITING FOR YOU HERE.

50:01.100 --> 50:03.295
KROEHNER WILL NEVER APPRECIATE
HOW GOOD YOU ARE, RICO.

50:03.300 --> 50:05.894
YOU'LL JUST BE A PART
OF THEIR ASSEMBLY LINE.

50:07.560 --> 50:09.118
WE'LL SEE.

50:13.630 --> 50:15.518
OH, WORD OF ADVICE,
GUYS...

50:15.530 --> 50:18.499
DON'T TURN YOUR
BACK ON GILARDI.

50:19.600 --> 50:21.898
WELL, SO MUCH
FOR LOYALTY.

50:21.900 --> 50:24.824
NATE, HE'S GIVEN US
FIVE YEARS.

50:24.830 --> 50:26.252
HE DOESN'T
OWE US ANYTHING.

50:26.260 --> 50:28.626
NOBODY OWES US.

50:34.330 --> 50:35.888
( knocking )

50:48.860 --> 50:51.454
MY ONLY DEFENSE IS
I THINK I WAS HALLUCINATING.

50:54.660 --> 50:57.788
THAT AND THE THOUGHT OF YOU
WITH ANOTHER MAN MAKES ME CRAZY.

50:57.800 --> 50:59.756
SORRY.

51:01.560 --> 51:04.120
I'M JUST A GUY
THAT WAY.

51:05.500 --> 51:07.252
SO, WHERE'S CONNOR ?

51:07.260 --> 51:08.750
OH, GOD,
I THREW HIM OUT.

51:08.760 --> 51:11.524
THERE'S ONLY SO MUCH
OF HIM I CAN TAKE.

51:13.500 --> 51:15.525
SO, YOU FORGIVE ME ?

51:15.530 --> 51:18.351
SURE, WHY NOT ?

51:18.360 --> 51:19.258
GOOD.

51:19.260 --> 51:21.797
NOW IT'S
YOUR TURN.

51:23.660 --> 51:25.389
YOU WANT ME
TO APOLOGIZE ?

51:25.400 --> 51:26.424
YES.

51:29.800 --> 51:32.598
FOR TRYING TO USE BILLY'S
MELTDOWN AND CONNOR'S VISIT

51:32.600 --> 51:34.556
TO PUSH ME AWAY.

51:34.560 --> 51:37.051
FOR BEING IMPATIENT
WITH MY VERY VALID

51:37.060 --> 51:39.199
EMOTIONAL RESPONSE
TO EACH ONE.

51:39.200 --> 51:42.351
AND FOR ALWAYS ASKING ME TO
ADJUST MY BEHAVIOR AND FEELINGS

51:42.360 --> 51:45.420
BUT NEVER BEING WILLING
TO DO THAT YOURSELF.

51:47.560 --> 51:49.619
OKAY, THAT'S FAIR.

51:51.330 --> 51:53.423
I APOLOGIZE.

51:55.160 --> 51:56.650
PART OF YOU
WANTS ME TO BAIL.

51:56.660 --> 52:00.596
YEAH, YOU'RE
PROBABLY RIGHT.

52:01.430 --> 52:02.829
WHY ?

52:07.500 --> 52:10.594
BECAUSE WE'VE ALREADY
GONE FURTHER THAN I HAVE

52:10.600 --> 52:12.818
WITH ANYBODY SINCE...

52:14.000 --> 52:16.218
SINCE A LONG
TIME AGO.

52:18.260 --> 52:21.957
BECAUSE EVERY TIME I'VE EVER
BELIEVED IN A HAPPY ENDING,

52:21.960 --> 52:25.350
I'VE GOTTEN
SEVERELY FUCKED.

52:27.360 --> 52:29.157
SORRY.

52:31.400 --> 52:33.459
WELL, DO ME
A FAVOR.

52:33.460 --> 52:36.099
PROMISE ME THAT
FROM HERE ON OUT

52:36.100 --> 52:38.898
I AM THE ONLY NAKED MAN
IN YOUR BED AND IN YOUR LIFE.

52:38.900 --> 52:41.221
I'M SERIOUS, BREN.

52:41.230 --> 52:43.323
PROMISE ME.

52:44.930 --> 52:47.490
I PROMISE.

52:47.900 --> 52:50.926
I LOVE YOU AND I WANT TO
BE WITH YOU FOR THE LONG HAUL.

52:50.930 --> 52:53.626
BUT THERE'S A LIMIT
TO THE AMOUNT OF SHIT
I WILL PUT UP WITH.

52:53.630 --> 52:56.758
DID YOU JUST MAKE ME
A LIFETIME COMMITMENT,

52:56.760 --> 52:59.422
RIGHT BEFORE THE THINLY-VEILED
THREAT OF ABANDONMENT ?

52:59.430 --> 53:03.696
WELL, I DON'T REMEMBER
USING THE WORD LIFETIME.

53:03.700 --> 53:06.555
OH, WELL, I WON'T
HOLD YOU TO IT.

53:14.700 --> 53:15.849
OH.

53:16.830 --> 53:21.096
SORRY I'M SO WEIRD
ABOUT INTIMACY.

53:23.060 --> 53:25.949
I GUESS SPENDING YOUR
CHILDHOOD BEING PICKED APART

53:25.960 --> 53:29.020
BY BEHAVIORAL PSYCHOLOGISTS
WILL DO THAT.

53:29.930 --> 53:33.320
YEAH, WELL, NOT BEING
ABLE TO SLEEP AT NIGHT

53:33.330 --> 53:35.218
BECAUSE YOU KNOW YOUR BASEMENT'S
FULL OF DEAD PEOPLE

53:35.230 --> 53:37.448
TAKES ITS TOLL TOO.

53:48.630 --> 53:51.394
( phone )

53:53.500 --> 53:55.559
SORRY.

54:00.000 --> 54:02.195
NATE FISHER.

54:02.200 --> 54:04.623
REMEMBER THAT CHARTERED BUS
THAT OVERTURNED LAST NIGHT ?

54:04.630 --> 54:06.222
THEY WERE
ALL LOCALS.

54:06.230 --> 54:07.697
WE'RE GETTING
THREE OF THEM.

54:07.700 --> 54:09.156
THE FIRST FAMILY
WILL BE HERE IN AN HOUR.

54:09.160 --> 54:11.196
I'M ON MY WAY.

54:11.200 --> 54:12.895
AND TRY TO CURB
YOUR ENTHUSIASM.

54:12.900 --> 54:14.697
THIS'LL BE TOUGH
WITHOUT RICO.

54:14.700 --> 54:16.349
See you later.

54:35.560 --> 54:38.222
GOOD LORD, WHAT DID
THEY DO TO YOU ?

54:38.230 --> 54:39.754
DON'T ASK.

54:45.530 --> 54:48.624
SO, DID MOM FREAK WHEN
YOU TOLD HER I GOT BUSTED ?

54:48.630 --> 54:51.224
I DIDN'T TELL HER.

54:52.930 --> 54:54.659
OKAY, WHY ?

54:54.660 --> 54:56.855
I DON'T KNOW,
OTHER STUFF CAME UP.

54:56.860 --> 54:59.590
IT SEEMED LIKE
A LOW PRIORITY.

54:59.600 --> 55:01.022
ARE YOU GOING TO ?

55:01.030 --> 55:02.588
PROBABLY NOT.

55:06.200 --> 55:07.929
I'M SORRY THE CROSSROADS
THING DIDN'T WORK OUT

55:07.930 --> 55:09.329
LIKE YOU HAD HOPED.

55:09.330 --> 55:11.890
ACTUALLY, IT WAS
KIND OF AMAZING.

55:11.900 --> 55:15.529
I THINK I REALLY LEARNED
SOMETHING VALUABLE.

55:17.260 --> 55:19.797
EVERYTHING I THINK
I KNOW IS WRONG.

55:28.200 --> 55:30.350
HEY, WHAT HAPPENED
TO THAT GUY KEITH ?

55:35.060 --> 55:36.857
IT JUST DIDN'T
WORK OUT.

55:41.730 --> 55:43.357
THAT'S TOO BAD.

55:43.360 --> 55:45.123
LIFE GOES ON.

55:48.930 --> 55:50.750
THAT IT DOES.

55:51.630 --> 55:53.029
WELL...

55:53.030 --> 55:55.157
THERE'S WORK
TO BE DONE.

